
Color Widgets for Qt
====================

The provided widgets are:

* Color_Wheel, An analog widget used to select a color
* Color_Preview, A simple widget that dislay a color
* Gradient_Slider, A slider that has a gradient background
* Color_Selector, A Color_Preview that shows a Color_Dialog when clicked
* Color_Dialog (not designer plugin) A dialog that uses the above widgets
    to provide a better user experience than QColorDialog

Installing as a Designer Plugin
-------------------------------

Compile the library and install in
(Qt SDK)/Tools/QtCreator/bin/designer/
(Qt SDK)/(Qt Version)/(Toolchain)/plugins/designer

 qmake && make && make install



Using them in your application
------------------------------

include color_widgets.pri


